    <string name="privacy_policy_content">Thank you for using WanAndroid!\nWe have updated our Privacy Policy according to the latest regulatory requirements. Please note:\n1. We collect and use necessary information to provide you with basic transaction functions;\n2. With your explicit authorization, we will obtain storage permission to save article sharing images. You have the right to refuse or cancel authorization;\n3. We take security measures to protect your information;\n4. Without your consent, we will not obtain, share, or provide your information to third parties.</string>

